  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK834">
<l>ōti yuṇarntum piṟarkkuraittun tāṉaṭaṅkāp</l>
<l>pētaiyiṟ pētaiyā ril</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are no greater fools than he who, though he has read and understood (a great deal) and even taught it to others, does not walk according to his own teaching.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
